Usage: write_power_intent [-help] <fileName> [-no_extra_connects] {-cpf | -1801 | -incremental_1801 } [{ -inst <string> | {-topHier -hierInst <string>}}]

-help                        # Prints out the command usage
<fileName>                   # output filename (string, required)
-1801                        # output file in IEEE1801 format (bool, required)
-cpf                         # output file in CPF format (bool, required)
-hierInst <string>           # list of hinsts (string, optional)
-incremental_1801            # incremental IEEE1801 power intent
                             # (bool, required)
-inst <string>               # inst name (string, optional)
-no_extra_connects           # do not write out extra gnc (csn)
                             # (bool, optional)
-topHier                     # is top hierarchy (bool, optional)